Per Project:

Defined in pom.xml
    Command Line -mvn package -S <path to setting file>

Per User:

    Defined in <user.home>/.m2/settings.xml

Global:

    Defined in <Maven Home>/conf/settings.xml

Use Project POM:

    when your build needs to be portable to other computers.
    When other may or may not need build features.

Use Setting.xml when:
    You want the profile available to many Projects
    Frequently used for configuration of repository manager.
    Protection of secrets
    enviornment configuration values
